    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842610/extras/78386211bcfec7ba3fda4e97c872f7c7.poster.avif?t=1763300199\" width=274 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842610/extras/78386211bcfec7ba3fda4e97c872f7c7.webm?t=1763300199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842610/extras/78386211bcfec7ba3fda4e97c872f7c7.mp4?t=1763300199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >巫师就是你！</h2>探索幽深地牢，收集传说圣物，精通强大法术，击败尽可能多的敌人！选择职业，踏上你的冒险吧！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2>《Dungeon Wizards》是一款 Rogue-lite 三消角色扮演游戏。只要将攻击型方块与敌人或头目方块连接起来，就能将其击败，赚得经验值，升级你的巫师。不过，三思后行、慎点技能是尽可能长久生存的不二法则！收集符文方块，学习强大法术，并发动法术削弱敌人、强化自身，完全掌控战场。匹配金币方块，就能解锁圣物，获得被动加成，如每回合额外经验点数，或发动法术后的额外属性点等。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 可玩教程，轻松入门<br></li><li> 3 种难度等级<br></li><li> 8 种职业，迥异玩法<br></li><li> 21 个拥有独特技能的头目<br></li><li> 45 种不同特性的圣物<br></li><li> 30 种水、火和土系法术<br></li><li> 挑战模式，带给你独特的挑战和特殊规则<br></li><li> 所有职业和难度等级均可查看排位和通产数据<br></li><li> 职业等级系统推进，解锁新技能、圣物和法术，带给你源源不断的动力<br></li><li> 访问合集索引，查看迄今已解锁的全部圣物、法术和头目<br></li><li> 多种成就等你冲击 </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842610/extras/d5fa5ca2d783c36a1bac685847d65580.poster.avif?t=1763300199\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842610/extras/d5fa5ca2d783c36a1bac685847d65580.webm?t=1763300199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842610/extras/d5fa5ca2d783c36a1bac685847d65580.mp4?t=1763300199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
